ITEM NO.801               COURT NO.13               SECTION XII-A
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition(s) for Special Leave to Appeal (C)  No(s).  16793/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated 09-06-2025
in WP No. 15398/2025 passed by the High Court for The State of
Telangana at Hyderabad]
AAYUSHI                                            Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
UNION OF INDIA & ORS.                              Respondent(s)
Date : 07-07-2025 This petition was mentioned today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE RAJESH BINDAL
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE R. MAHADEVAN
For Petitioner(s) : 
Mr. A.D.N.Rao,Sr.Adv. (Mentioned by)
Mr. Ashutosh Dubey, AOR                   
For Respondent(s) : 
Ms. Archana Pathak Dave,ASG
Mr. Sudarshan Lamba, AOR
Ms. Pankhuri Shrivzastava,Adv.
Ms. Neelam Sharma, AOR                   
UPON being mentioned the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
Learned senior counsel appearing for the petitioner
mentioned the matter for correction of the order dated 4 th
July, 2025.  
The prayer made by the learned senior counsel for
the  petitioner  is  accepted  to  the  extent  that  in
paragraph 2 of the order passed on that day towards the
end, the following words shall be added:
‘in the State of Telangana’.
(ANITA MALHOTRA)                           (SAPNA BANSAL)
 AR-CUM-PS                                 COURT MASTER
